{"tid":1425522,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"〔突發〕 有關反中亂港外國勢力物資輸送渠道","createTime":"2019-08-06T18:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:39:12.000Z","uid":300420,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ff1e18a89d4daec050e0c256fdfb7a265c587a14","tid":1425522,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:32:54.000Z","msg":"話說小弟一向忠黨愛國， 為祖國做臥底， 平日深入敵陣， 喺網絡視察敵情， 點知竟然比我見到反華勢力透過網絡輸出暴動材料，搞亂香港， 就喺度公告天下，等人民認往你班冚家產先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n睇下呢個面具：<a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/itm/Gas-Mask-Single-Filter-Fan-CS-Edition-Perspiration-Dust-Face-Guard-Breathable/312719942265?hash=item48cf8fa279:g:JX8AAOSwH2ldQqqM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ebay.com%2Fitm%2FGas-Mask-Single-Filter-Fan-CS-Edition-Perspiration-Dust-Face-Guard-Breathable%2F312719942265%3Fhash%3Ditem48cf8fa279%3Ag%3AJX8AAOSwH2ldQqqM&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZiwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=11216e0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ebay.com/itm/Gas-Mask-Single-Filter-Fan-CS-Edition-Perspiration-Dust-Face-Guard-Breathable/312719942265?hash=item48cf8fa279:g:JX8AAOSwH2ldQqqM</a><br />\n<br />\n包到咁實做乜， 做得嘢就預咗畀人影， <span style=\"color: red;\">又扑人又噴嘢又冇編號又唔敢上鏡，咁驚就唔好出街啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再睇下呢支雷射筆：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/itm/High-Power-Blue-Laser-Pointers-5000000m-Lazer-Flashlight-Burning/312665394907?hash=item48cc4f4edb:g:VE8AAOSwvT5dC4b9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ebay.com%2Fitm%2FHigh-Power-Blue-Laser-Pointers-5000000m-Lazer-Flashlight-Burning%2F312665394907%3Fhash%3Ditem48cc4f4edb%3Ag%3AVE8AAOSwvT5dC4b9&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZiwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=3d49ce40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ebay.com/itm/High-Power-Blue-Laser-Pointers-5000000m-Lazer-Flashlight-Burning/312665394907?hash=item48cc4f4edb:g:VE8AAOSwvT5dC4b9</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所有出到光嘅嘢都係攻擊性武器嚟， 勁過催淚彈，海綿彈， 胡椒彈</span>， 你仲唔係向反華勢力提供物資，試圖發動暴亂？<br />\n<br />\n嚇到我即刻同上級匯報， 佢話冇問題， 呢啲嘢過唔到海關， 而公安同志亦會據地址上門處理 ，但其實唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 大家睇下呢則新聞: <a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://news.tvbs.com.tw/entry/475836&amp;ved=2ahUKEwioq8GH7O7jAhWLF4gKHSz6CUAQFjACegQIBBAB&amp;usg=AOvVaw0xXO63kFT9kPeBIq3amubg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fentry%2F475836%26ved%3D2ahUKEwioq8GH7O7jAhWLF4gKHSz6CUAQFjACegQIBBAB%26usg%3DAOvVaw0xXO63kFT9kPeBIq3amubg&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZiwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=28253b43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://news.tvbs.com.tw/entry/475836&amp;ved=2ahUKEwioq8GH7O7jAhWLF4gKHSz6CUAQFjACegQIBBAB&amp;usg=AOvVaw0xXO63kFT9kPeBIq3amubg</a><br />\n<br />\n如果反華勢力先將暴動物資分拆再寄嚟香港， 海關真係分唔出， <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">槍</span></span>都運到就知乜事， 淨係 毅進精英先有理智可以揸槍㗎， 畀班暴徒攞到仲得了， <span style=\"color: red;\">而且只要將送貨地址改做啲咩廢屋， 碼頭， 之後再去收貨， 公安就無法將其繩之於法</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點算呀， 上級唔聽， 我唯有喺度開po， 理智嘅大家千祈唔好上去買嘢， 唔好叫賣家拆散， 唔好分享比班暴徒聽， 做個良好市民， 維護國家尊嚴， 抵制顏色革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b632c10418e5c2eaf6c54e5eb8ed45134f21dc","tid":1425522,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:33:47.000Z","msg":"愛港愛國 輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28809ea9c9c6e7b5143d2bd85539a35d8eeaf7f","tid":1425522,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:33:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743852bc4a18e5226722062fafa6477b637f256c","tid":1425522,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:34:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963110dca1009692bd7b21fa507632df5c77f7f3","tid":1425522,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:34:35.000Z","msg":"十連之推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21fd30651b08d742de613fd4f30704c1a594f68","tid":1425522,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:34:46.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"4abbe119548fe70d751c30a8c170e8edf6c3e14b","tid":1425522,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:34:56.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"bc490a2566cf8b335a46312ad5c81f22666fd962","tid":1425522,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:35:06.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c88a6c79b466e29c8179bc360673c9f5b0f82134","tid":1425522,"uid":160964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:35:17.000Z","msg":"P牌收皮啦，又推人去死"},{"pid":"b643e854abca0392339a07ddcdcb7ec4328af069","tid":1425522,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:35:24.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"6ed1692d466c188a35fc2ba0af1a57b5cac9e9c0","tid":1425522,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cfeebec04d6146d9cf5820a9a0973c6d365f88","tid":1425522,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:38:23.000Z","msg":"咁易買槍，周街都係槍啦<br />\n你買黎睇下"},{"pid":"36efc737f512263af4227026a70fd26de68d96e9","tid":1425522,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3cfeebec04d6146d9cf5820a9a0973c6d365f88","tid":1425522,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike